<i>noun</i>: 누더기 [누더기], 남루 [남ː누], 걸레 [걸레] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>누더기 [누더기]</dt><br>
<dd>rags; tatters</dd><br>
<dd>해지고 찢어진 곳을 여러 헝겊으로 어지럽게 기워 놓은 더러운 옷이나 천.</dd><br>
<dd>Dirty cloth or clothes, whose worn or torn part is covered with another cloth and sewn messily.</dd><br>
<dt>남루 [남ː누]</dt><br>
<dd>rags; shabby clothes</dd><br>
<dd>때 묻고 낡은 더러운 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>Stained, dirty, worn-out clothes.</dd><br>
<dt>걸레 [걸레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. damp cloth; dusting cloth</dd><br>
<dd>더러운 것이나 물기를 닦는 데 쓰는 헝겊.</dd><br>
<dd>A cloth used to wipe stains or water off.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rags; junk</dd><br>
<dd>더럽고 낡은 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>A dirty and old thing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>